      C\ar [rr, ""{name=F, below}, "F"]\ar [dr, "K"'] && E \\
      & D\ar [ur, "\operatorname *{Ran}_K F"']\makebox [0pt][l]{,}
      \ar [Rightarrow, from=2-2, to=F, "\epsilon "]
    \end {tikzcd}


 that is universal in that for any other pair D\xrightarrow {G} E and
  GK\xrightarrow {\delta } F, \delta  factors uniquely through \epsilon : 




